n0:createSxmlObject.n0:source: <VIEW xmlns="http://xmlns.oracle.com/ku" version="1.0"> <SCHEMA>CHINOOK</SCHEMA> <NAME>JV$TRACK</NAME> <DEFAULT_COLLATION>USING_NLS_COMP</DEFAULT_COLLATION> <COL_LIST> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>JRN_FLAG</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>JRN_SUBSCRIBER</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>JRN_DATE</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>TRACKID</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>NAME</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>ALBUMID</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>MEDIATYPEID</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>GENREID</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>COMPOSER</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>MILLISECONDS</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>BYTES</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> <COL_LIST_ITEM> <NAME>UNITPRICE</NAME> </COL_LIST_ITEM> </COL_LIST> <SUBQUERY>select decode(TARG.ROWID, null, 'D', 'I') JRN_FLAG, JRN.JRN_SUBSCRIBER JRN_SUBSCRIBER, JRN.JRN_DATE JRN_DATE, JRN.TRACKID TRACKID, TARG.NAME NAME, TARG.ALBUMID ALBUMID, TARG.MEDIATYPEID MEDIATYPEID, TARG.GENREID GENREID, TARG.COMPOSER COMPOSER, TARG.MILLISECONDS MILLISECONDS, TARG.BYTES BYTES, TARG.UNITPRICE UNITPRICE from ( select L.JRN_SUBSCRIBER JRN_SUBSCRIBER, L.TRACKID TRACKID, max(L.JRN_DATE) JRN_DATE from CHINOOK.J$TRACK L where L.JRN_CONSUMED = '1' group by L.JRN_SUBSCRIBER, L.TRACKID ) JRN, CHINOOK.TRACK TARG where JRN.TRACKID = TARG.TRACKID (+)</SUBQUERY> </VIEW>
